  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dad \u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9c \u0db8\u0ddd\u0dc3\u0db8 \u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Southwest Monsoon is active from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, activation of southwest monsoon conditions is expected from tomorrow (01).",
        "Accordingly, the department said that an increase in rain conditions is expected in the south-western part of the island (West, Sabaragamuwa, Central provinces and Galle and Matara districts) and an increase in wind speed in the western slopes of the central mountains and in the western and southern provinces."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "tomorrow",
          "label": "DATE"
        }
      ],
